latestIgtvVideos.title: Checking in with fellow makeup artists since going back to work
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I felt the need to make a quick video and somehow thought a no makeup, no sleep, greasy hair and yesterday’s shirt looks was the way to go 😑. 
We need to talk about Covid. Specifically going back to work and some of the things you can do to keep yourself safe, healthy and happy. If you know better than me and i misspoke or interpreted the data wrong, please don’t hesitate to correct me! 
Also, please forgive my California accent, i realize it went completely unchecked and off the rails in this video. Oof. 
Xxx #makeup #covid19 #makeupartist

latestIgtvVideos.title: •THE SHOWGIRL•
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Day 6 of my Making Faces challenge and I’ve run out of wigs to recreate some of the other looks myself (if any wig companies wanna send me a Marilyn wig that’d be great 😂) so here is my husband as The Showgirl! Thanks for being such a great sport @stadelaf even though I taped your face so tight it hurt to breath and all the makeup made you itchy. Final result is in the previous post on my page. Hope you like! #makingfaces #kevynaucoin #drag #selfisolation #asmr
